952
01:07:36,170 --> 01:07:39,014
Di mana kecap dan wasabinya?

953
01:07:39,939 --> 01:07:41,044
Di sini.

954
01:07:43,939 --> 01:07:46,485
Bukankah setidaknya aku berhak

955
01:07:47,109 --> 01:07:50,485
